  <para style="mt1">Sofoni</para>
  <para style="im">Mosakoli Sofoni oyo molongo na ye ya mbotama ezalaki molayi (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 1:1">1.1</ref></char>) akokaki kozala moto ya libota ya bokonzi. Kati na bakoko na ye, ezalaki na moto moko na kombo « Ezekiasi » oyo azalaki mokonzi : akonzaki Yuda kobanda na mobu 715 kino na mobu 698 to 686 liboso ete Yesu-Klisto abotama.</para>
  <para style="ip">Sofoni azalaki momemi sango ya Yawe kati na bokonzi ya Yuda, na tango Joziasi azalaki mokonzi (640–609). Bakonzi oyo balekaki liboso na ye, Manase mpe Amoni, balendisaki bato ete bamipesa na kosambela banzambe ya bikeko (<char style="xt"><ref loc="2KI 21">2Ba 21</ref></char>). Na mobu 629 to 628, Joziasi amipesaki na mosala ya kolongola na mboka banzambe, bikeko mpe bisika ya bule oyo elongobanaki te kolanda Mobeko ya Nzambe (<char style="xt"><ref loc="2CH 34:3-7">2Ma 34.3-7</ref></char>). Na mobu 622, abongisisaki Tempelo oyo ezalaki ekangama. Kati na yango, ezalaki na Mobeko ya Moyize oyo babosana. Mpo ete Mobeko ya Moyize emonanaki, Joziasi akotisaki mbongwana monene (<char style="xt"><ref loc="2CH 34:8-33">2Ma 34.8-33</ref></char>) oyo esungamaki na kokweya ya Asiri, bokonzi oyo ezalaki kokonza etuka wana nyonso.</para>
  <para style="ip">Sofoni asalaki mosala na ye liboso ya mbongwana ya mobu 622, pamba te alobaki lisusu ete bato bazalaki kosambela banzambe ya bikeko kati na Yuda mpe na Yelusalemi (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 1:4-5">1.4-5</ref></char>) ; mpe mobeko ya Ninive, engumba mokonzi ya Asiri, ezalaki kaka kokamba etuka mobimba (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 2:13-15">2.13-15</ref></char>). Lisakoli epesamaki liboso ya kokweyisama ya nguya ya Asiri : kokweyisama ya nguya ya Asiri esalemaki sima na kufa ya Asuribanipali, na mobu 625. Boye, tokoki koloba ete Sofoni asalaki mosala na ye na mobu pene 630 ; azalaki mosika te na mosala ya Joziasi ya kolongola kati na Yuda mpe Yelusalemi losambo epai ya banzambe ya bikeko, na mobu 629 to 628.</para>
  <para style="ip">Sofoni asakolaki boyei ya mokolo ya Yawe (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 1:2-2:3">1.2–2.3</ref></char>). Na mokolo yango, Nzambe akosambisa kati na bato na Ye basambeli ya banzambe ya bikeko. Kaka bato na komikitisa, ba-oyo batiaka elikya na bango kati na Yawe mpe babikaka bomoi na bango kolanda bosembo nde bakobika (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 2:3">2.3</ref></char>) : ezali te mpo ete bilaka ya Nzambe ekokokisama te, kasi mpo ete lobiko ezalaka kolanda ngolu ya Nzambe. Mokolo yango ya Yawe ezalaki mpe mpo na bikolo oyo ezalaki zingazinga ya Yuda, mpe mpo na Ninive, liboso ete ekomela Yelusalemi (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 2:4-3:8">2.4–3.8</ref></char>). Nzokande Yawe akosala kaka te lokola Mosambisi, kasi akoya mpe mpo na kobikisa (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 3:9-20">3.9-20</ref></char>). Na nzela ya mosala na Ye ya kobongola, bikolo ekosalela Ye na boyokani (<char style="xt"><ref loc="ZEP 3:9">3.9</ref></char>). Lokola mpe kosambisama ekozala lokola kiyungulu, batikali ya Isalaele bakobongwana mpe bakotika misala mabe. Bongo Yawe akotelema na kati-kati ya bato na Ye, lokola Mosambisi te mpo na kokatela bango etumbu kasi lokola mobundi mpo na kobikisa bango.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="ZEP 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Mokolo ya Yawe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:1"/>Na tango Joziasi, mwana mobali ya Amoni, azalaki mokonzi ya mokili ya Yuda, Yawe alobaki na Sofoni, mwana mobali ya Kushi, mwana mobali ya Gedalia, mwana mobali ya Amaria, mwana mobali ya Ezekiasi :<verse eid="ZEP 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:2"/>« Nakosilisa kobebisa biloko nyonso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:2">oyo ezali kati na mokili, »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:2">elobi Yawe,<verse eid="ZEP 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:3"/>« solo, nakoboma ezala bato to banyama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:3">ezala bandeke ya likolo to bambisi ya ebale ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:3">nakolongola, na mokili, bato mabe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:3">mpe biloko oyo ebetisaka bato mabaku »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:3">elobi Yawe.<verse eid="ZEP 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya mokili ya Yuda</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:4"/>« Nakosembola loboko na Ngai</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:4">mpo na kopesa mokili ya Yuda</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:4">mpe bavandi nyonso ya Yelusalemi etumbu ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:4">nakosilisa koboma, na esika oyo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:4">nyonso oyo etikali, ya losambo ya nzambe Bala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:4">elongo na bakombo ya banganga-nzambe ya bapagano,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:4">oyo basalelaka banzambe ya bikeko :<verse eid="ZEP 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:5"/>bato nyonso oyo bafukamaka na likolo ya bandako</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:5">mpo na kosambela mampinga ya likolo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:5">bato nyonso oyo bagumbamaka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:5">na kolapa ndayi na Kombo na Yawe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:5">mpe na kombo na nzambe Moloki,<verse eid="ZEP 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:6"/>bato nyonso oyo bapesaka Yawe mokongo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:6">oyo balukaka Ye te mpe batunaka Ye te.<verse eid="ZEP 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:7"/>Bovanda kimia liboso ya Nkolo Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:7">pamba te mokolo ya Yawe ekomi pene !</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:7">Yawe abongisi mbeka,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:7">abulisi babengami na Ye.<verse eid="ZEP 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:8"/>Na mokolo ya mbeka ya Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:8">nakopesa etumbu epai ya bakambi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:8">epai ya bana mibali ya mokonzi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:8">mpe epai ya bato nyonso oyo balataka bilamba ya bapaya.<verse eid="ZEP 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:9"/>Na mokolo wana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:9">nakopesa etumbu epai ya bato nyonso</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:9">oyo bapumbwaka ekotelo ya tempelo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:9">bato oyo batondisaka tempelo ya banzambe na bango ya bikeko</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:9">na makambo ya kanza mpe na lokuta.<verse eid="ZEP 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:10"/>Na mokolo wana, »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:10">elobi Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:10">« koganga makasi ekoyokana</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:10">wuta na Ekuke ya Bambisi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:10">kolela ekoyokana wuta na Mboka ya sika</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:10">mpe lokito monene wuta na bangomba mikuse.<verse eid="ZEP 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:11"/>Bino bavandi ya etuka Makiteshi, bolela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:11">pamba te bato nyonso ya mombongo bakokufa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:11">mpe bato nyonso oyo batekaka palata bakobebisama !<verse eid="ZEP 1:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:12"/>Na tango wana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:12">nakoluka engumba Yelusalemi na nzela ya mwinda,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:12">nakopesa etumbu epai ya bato nyonso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:12">oyo bamimonaka ete bakoka mpe bamilobelaka :</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:12">‹ Yawe asalaka na Ye eloko te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:12">ezala ya malamu to ya mabe. ›<verse eid="ZEP 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:13"/>Bakobotola bango bomengo na makasi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:13">mpe bakobuka bandako na bango ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:13">bakotonga bandako, kasi bakotikala kovanda yango te ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:13">bakosala bilanga ya vino,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:13">kasi bakotikala komela vino na yango te. »<verse eid="ZEP 1:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Mokolo ya Yawe</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:14"/>Mokolo monene ya Yawe ekomi pene,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:14">solo ekomi pene mpe ezali koya noki penza.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:14">Boyoka ! Makelele ya mokolo na Yawe ekozala bololo ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:14">ezala basoda ya mpiko, bakoganga mpo na koluka lisungi.<verse eid="ZEP 1:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:15"/>Mokolo yango ekozala mokolo ya kanda makasi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:15">mokolo ya pasi mpe ya somo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:15">mokolo ya komitungisa mpe ya kobebisama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:15">mokolo ya butu mpe ya molili makasi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:15">mokolo ya mapata mpe mapata ya mwindo,<verse eid="ZEP 1:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:16"/>mokolo ya kobeta bakelelo mpe ya makelele ya bitumba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:16">mpo na kobundisa bingumba batonga makasi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:16">mpe bandako milayi oyo batonga makasi.<verse eid="ZEP 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:17"/>Nakotindela bato pasi ya makasi :</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:17">bakokoma kotambola lokola bato balangwe masanga,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:17">pamba te basalaki masumu liboso ya Yawe ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:17">bakopanza makila na bango lokola putulu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:17">mpe bakobwaka misopo na bango lokola salite.<verse eid="ZEP 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ZEP 1:18"/>Na mokolo ya kanda na Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:18">ezala palata to wolo na bango ekobikisa bango te.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="ZEP 1:18"/>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:18">Na moto ya zuwa na Ye,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:18">mokili mobimba ekozikisama,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 1:18">pamba te akosukisa na mbalakata</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 1:18">bavandi nyonso ya mokili.<verse eid="ZEP 1:18"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ZEP 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="ZEP 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Kobengama ya bato oyo batalelaka Yawe</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:1"/>Oh ekolo oyo eyokaka soni te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:1">bosangana nanu bino nyonso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:1">mpe bokanisa malamu<verse eid="ZEP 2:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:2"/>liboso ete mokolo oyo ekatama</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:2">mpo na kosambisama ekoka,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:2">liboso ete mokolo yango eleka lokola matiti ya loso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:2">oyo mopepe ememi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:2">mpe liboso ete kanda mpe kotomboka ya Yawe ekomela bino !<verse eid="ZEP 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:3"/>Boluka Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:3">bino bato nyonso ya komikitisa kati na mokili,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:3">bino oyo bokokisaka mitindo na Ye !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:3">Boluka kotambola na bosembo mpe na komikitisa !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:3">Tango mosusu bokobika</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:3">na mokolo ya kanda ya Yawe.<verse eid="ZEP 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya Filisitia</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:4"/>Bakosundola engumba Gaza,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:4">bongo engumba Ashikeloni ekobebisama ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:4">bakobengana bato ya engumba Asidodi na makasi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:4">mpe bakopikola engumba Ekroni.<verse eid="ZEP 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:5"/>Mawa na bino bavandi ya etuka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:5">oyo ezali pembeni ya ebale monene,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:5">bino bato ya Kereti !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:5">Pamba te Liloba na Yawe etelemeli bino :</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:5">« Kanana, mokili ya bato ya Filisitia,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:5">nakobebisa yo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:5">mpe moto ata moko te akotikala kati na yo. »<verse eid="ZEP 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:6"/>Etuka oyo ezali pembeni ya ebale monene,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:6">epai wapi bato ya Kreti bavandaka,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:6">ekokoma esika ya babateli bibwele</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:6">mpe lopango ya kobokola bibwele.<verse eid="ZEP 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:7"/>Ekokoma etuka ya batikali ya libota ya Yuda ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:7">bakokuta kuna bisika ya kobokola bibwele na bango.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:7">Pokwa nyonso, bakolala na bandako ya Ashikeloni,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:7">pamba te Yawe, Nzambe na bango, akobatela bango,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:7">akobongisa lisusu bomoi ya bato na bango,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:7">oyo bakowuta na bowumbu.<verse eid="ZEP 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya mokili ya Moabi mpe ya Amoni</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:8"/>« Nayokaki bato ya Moabi kofinga bato na Ngai</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:8">mpe ndenge bato ya Amoni bazalaki kotiola</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:8">mpe koluka kobotola mabele na bango.<verse eid="ZEP 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:9"/>Yango wana, na Kombo na Ngai, »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:9">elobi Yawe, Mokonzi ya mampinga, Nzambe ya Isalaele,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:9">« Moabi ekokoma penza lokola Sodome,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:9">mpe bato ya Amoni bakokoma lokola Gomore ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:9">ekokoma esika oyo ebotaka matiti mabe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:9">esika ya mabulu ya mungwa,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:9">esika ebebisama mpo na libela.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:9">Batikali na Ngai bakobotola bango bomengo na makasi,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:9">mpe batikali ya ekolo na Ngai bakozwa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:9">mikili yango lokola libula. »<verse eid="ZEP 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:10"/>Wana nde lifuti oyo bakozwa mpo na lolendo na bango, pamba te bafingaki mpe batiolaki bato ya Yawe, Mokonzi ya mampinga. <verse eid="ZEP 2:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:11"/>Yawe akoyokisa bango somo tango akobebisa banzambe ya bikeko nyonso ya mabele. Bato ya bikolo nyonso bakogumbamela Ye na bisika nyonso, moto na moto na esika oyo akozala kati na mokili na ye.<verse eid="ZEP 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya Kushi</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:12"/>Bino mpe bato ya Kushi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:12">bokokufa na mopanga na ngai.<verse eid="ZEP 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya Asiri</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:13"/>Akosembola loboko na Ye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:13">mpo na kobundisa etuka ya nor,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:13">akobebisa Asiri</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:13">akobebisa penza Ninive mobimba</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:13">mpe akokawusa yango lokola esobe.<verse eid="ZEP 2:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:14"/>Ekokoma esika oyo bitonga</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:14">mpe banyama ya ndenge na ndenge ekokoma kolala.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:14">Esulungutu mpe kombekombe ekokoma kolekisa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:14">butu na yango na basonge ya bandako na yango.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:14">Kolela na yango ekoyokana kino na maninisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:14">libebi na libebi nde ekomonana</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:14">na bikotelo ya bandako,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:14">mpe mabaya ya banzete ya sedele ekotikala polele.<verse eid="ZEP 2:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ZEP 2:15"/>Tala ndenge ekosuka, engumba oyo ya bisengo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:15">oyo ezalaki na kimia koleka mpe ezalaki komilobela :</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:15">« Ezali nde ngai, mosusu azali te soki ngai te. »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:15">Ndenge nini engumba oyo ebebisami,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 2:15">ndenge nini ekomi penza ndako ya banyama !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:15">Bato nyonso oyo bakolekela wana</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 2:15">bakobeta piololo mpe koningisa mito.<verse eid="ZEP 2:15"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ZEP 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="ZEP 3"/>
  <para style="s1">Etumbu ya engumba Yelusalemi</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:1"/>Mawa na engumba ya batomboki,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:1">engumba ya makambo ya mbindo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:1">mpe engumba oyo enyokolaka bato !<verse eid="ZEP 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:2"/>Etosaka moto te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:2">endimaka pamela te,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:2">etiaka elikya na Yawe te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:2">epusanaka pene ya Nzambe na yango te.<verse eid="ZEP 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:3"/>Bakalaka na yango bazali lokola bankosi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:3">oyo ezali koganga ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:3">bakambi na yango bazali</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:3">lokola bambwa ya zamba oyo esalaka bokila na pokwa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:3">bongo etikaka ata eloko moko te na tongo.<verse eid="ZEP 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:4"/>Basakoli na yango bazali</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:4">bato ya lolendo mpe ya lokuta.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:4">Banganga-Nzambe na yango babebisaka</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:4">Esika ya bule mpe batosaka mibeko te.<verse eid="ZEP 3:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:5"/>Kati na engumba yango,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:5">Yawe azali sembo, asalaka mabe te ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:5">mokolo na mokolo, alakisaka bosembo na Ye</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:5">mpe azangaka te kokokisa yango tongo na tongo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:5">Nzokande, moto oyo atambolaka na bosembo te</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:5">amonaka likambo ya soni te.<verse eid="ZEP 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:6"/>Nabomi bato ya bikolo mosusu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:6">bandako na bango ya makasi ebebisami.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:6">Nasali ete babalabala na bango</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:6">etikala lisusu na bato te</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:6">mpo ete moto moko te alekela lisusu wana.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:6">Bingumba na bango ebebisami,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:6">ata moto moko te atikali lisusu kuna.<verse eid="ZEP 3:6"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:7"/>Namilobelaki boye na tina na engumba oyo :</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:7">« Solo, okobanga Ngai mpe okondima pamela na Ngai ! »</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:7">Boye bandako na yango ekobukana lisusu te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:7">mpe nakotindela yango lisusu etumbu moko te.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:7">Kasi atako bongo, bakobaki kaka kosala</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:7">misala na bango ya mabe.<verse eid="ZEP 3:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:8"/>Yango wana, « bozela Ngai, »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:8">elobi Yawe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:8">« bozela Ngai na mokolo oyo nakoya</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:8">mpo na kosamba elongo na bino ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:8">nazwaki mokano ya kosangisa</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:8">bato ya bikolo nyonso mpe ya mikili nyonso</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:8">mpo na kosopela bango kanda na Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:8">makasi nyonso penza ya kanda na Ngai :</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:8">mokili mobimba ekozika na moto</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:8">ya nguya ya kanda na Ngai.<verse eid="ZEP 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Litomba ya etumbu</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:9"/>Boye nakopetola bibebu ya bato ya bikolo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:9">mpo ete bango nyonso bazala ya kokoka</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:9">mpo na kobelela Kombo ya Yawe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:9">mpe kosalela Ye na motema mobimba.<verse eid="ZEP 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:10"/>Longwa na likolo ya bibale ya Kushi,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:10">bato na Ngai, oyo bagumbamelaka Ngai ;</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:10">bato na Ngai, oyo bapalangana bipai na bipai,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:10">bakomemela Ngai makabo.<verse eid="ZEP 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:11"/>Na mokolo wana, oh bato na Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:11">bokoyokisama lisusu soni te</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:11">mpo na mabe nyonso oyo bosalaki Ngai,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:11">pamba te nakolongola bato</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:11">oyo bamimatisaka na lolendo kati na bino.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:11">Boye bokomitombola lisusu te na lolendo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:11">na ngomba na Ngai ya bule.<verse eid="ZEP 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:12"/>Kasi kati na bino, nakotika bato oyo bakelela,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:12">bato oyo batambolaka na komikitisa,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:12">bato oyo bakozwa ebombamelo kati na Kombo na Yawe.<verse eid="ZEP 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:13"/>Batikali ya Isalaele bakosala lisusu mabe te,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:13">bakokosa lisusu te</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:13">to lokuta ekozala lisusu te kati na minoko na bango.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:13">Bakolia mpe bakolala na kimia,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:13">mpe moto moko te akobangisa bango lisusu.<verse eid="ZEP 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:14"/>Siona, mboka kitoko, yemba nzembo !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:14">Isalaele, ganga makasi !</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:14">Yelusalemi, mboka kitoko, sepela ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:14">mpe tika ete motema na yo etonda na esengo !<verse eid="ZEP 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:15"/>Yawe alongoli etumbu na yo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:15">mpe akimisi banguna na yo.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:15">Yawe, Mokonzi ya Isalaele, azali elongo na yo ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:15">kobanga lisusu pasi moko te.<verse eid="ZEP 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:16"/>Na mokolo wana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:16">bakoloba na Yelusalemi :</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:16">‹ Oh Siona, kobanga te !</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:16">Tika ete maboko na yo elemba te !<verse eid="ZEP 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:17"/>Yawe, Nzambe na yo, azali elongo na yo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:17">azali Elombe Mobikisi.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:17">Akosepela na yo makasi</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:17">mpe akopemisa yo, na bolingo na Ye ;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:17">akoyemba banzembo ya esengo na tina na yo. ›<verse eid="ZEP 3:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:18"/>Lokola na mikolo ya bafeti oyo ekatama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:18">nakolongola pasi kati na yo</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:18">mpo ete ozala lisusu na soni te.<verse eid="ZEP 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:19"/>Na tango wana, nakobeta bato nyonso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:19">oyo banyokolaki yo,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:19">nakosunga moto oyo atambolaka tengu-tengu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:19">mpe nakosangisa bato oyo bapanzana bipai na bipai.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:19">Nakopesa bango lokumu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:19">mpe nakosala ete sango na bango</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:19">epanzana na mikili nyonso</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:19">epai wapi basambwisaki bango.<verse eid="ZEP 3:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="ZEP 3:20"/>Na tango wana, nakosangisa bino,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:20">nakozongisa bino na mokili na bino.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:20">Nakopesa bino lokumu</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:20">mpe nakosala ete sango na bino epanzana</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:20">kati na bato ya bikolo nyonso ya mokili</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:20">tango, na miso na bino, nakozongisa bato na bino,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="ZEP 3:20">oyo bakendeki na bowumbu, »</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="ZEP 3:20">elobi Yawe.<verse eid="ZEP 3:20"/></para>
  <chapter eid="ZEP 3"/>
</usx>
